            "kjv_def": "anger, indignation,\n vengeance, wrath.",
            "pspeech": "N-GFS",
            "description": " properly, desire (as a reaching forth or excitement of the mind), i.e. (by analogy), violent passion (ire, or (justifiable) abhorrence); by implication punishment"
        },
