            "description": " used only in certain past tenses, the others being borrowed from the equivalent \u1f40\u03c0\u03c4\u1f71\u03bd\u03bf\u03bc\u03b1\u03b9(opt\u00e1nomai) and \u1f41\u03c1\u1f71\u03c9(hor\u00e1\u014d); properly, to see (literally or figuratively); by implication, (in the perfect tense only) to know"
        },
